    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/205f04287235dff42fa9ef666b0a0519.poster.avif?t=1666378010\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/205f04287235dff42fa9ef666b0a0519.webm?t=1666378010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/205f04287235dff42fa9ef666b0a0519.mp4?t=1666378010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>用自己的方式玩，每位英雄都有 3 种不同的卡片类别，攻击、防御和实用性。你可以组建最适合你游戏风格的组合。<br><br>每个类别也有自己的遗物，可以进一步增强你的游戏玩法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高级符文系统</h2>使用高级符文系统增强你的甲板，为你的卡片增添独特的天赋。这使得牌组结构具有无限的可能性。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >腐败</h2>世界一直在与腐败作斗争，腐败会随着时间的流逝而变得越来越强大，并将疾病应用于你们的世界。这些疾病会直接影响战斗和游戏难度，因为疾病的数量会随着每个满月（7 天）而增加。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >昼夜循环</h2>制定战略并为战斗之夜做好准备。黄昏时分，夜间怪物出现，黑色门户打开。如果你赢得夜战，可以获得独家奖励！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/aa70ee2120755ff5490367b2fca3421b.poster.avif?t=1666378010\" width=616 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/aa70ee2120755ff5490367b2fca3421b.webm?t=1666378010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/aa70ee2120755ff5490367b2fca3421b.mp4?t=1666378010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>天气事件<br>下雨，沙尘暴，暴风雪。有些事件可能使你受益，但其他事件可能会结束你的战斗，注意并利用好它们<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687740/extras/7e23a37074fa68739f461724a7a78460.poster.avif?t=1666378010\" width=616 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st